edu.proz.checkers.server.controller

Class SessionController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.proz.checkers.server.controller.SessionController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class SessionController
extends Object
implements Runnable
    Game session controller class. Runnable. Processes clients' requests, updates game state and provides responds for the clients. Contains private Command-type classes for processing polymorphic messages.
    Author:
    bartlomiej
